Ranger Help for: stalk
======================

SYNTAX:      stalk <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     20
SKILL TYPE:  stealth

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to shadow a target, following them with
partial concealment. While stalking, the Ranger gains a bonus to hit
on their next attack against the stalked target. The Ranger remains
partially hidden from other creatures but is not fully invisible.
Stalking is broken if the Ranger attacks a different target or is
detected. This skill combines elements of stealth and combat
preparation, making it useful for setting up an opening strike.
